Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:36.56,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}透き通る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:39.61,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}光の粒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:47.55,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}混じり気のない思い　残るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:50.00,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}二人でいると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.21,0:22:52.19,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}胸が熱いね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:57.25,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}嘘の付けない君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:22:59.64,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}夢が破れて
