Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面要讀哪本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前段時間大量的推理小說完好無損地漂流到了島上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實有件事我一直想做做看  哪怕就一次也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實  就是像推理小說中的主人公那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想試著真正去和怪人決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去解決事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想以此為藍本來寫小說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是清正先生的話應該能寫好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請一定寫一下試試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會期待著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我沒有文采的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:25.42,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,去揭秘吧  偵探（後篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我之名為紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話那邀請帖果然是你發的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那綾音所看到的我  也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  百面怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想聽到年輕少女的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:02:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想看到她們恐怖的表情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先在那少女的皮膚上塗了島上最癢的東部森林的山藥汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然會自然好轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過得要一周時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想立刻就治好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能使用這解毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快點把那個拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…居然對我重要的客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你作為敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進行排除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要解毒藥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在滿月還未消失之前抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼做的話  就全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙真靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  不能這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的聲音是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是朔夜小姐把什麼當作敵人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐照顧周到特意為我們放的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊洗澡一邊看煙花也是很享受的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是紅夜叉但也是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好像被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能躲開我的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是敵人但也值得欽佩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  先回月見亭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不認為事件會就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人好遲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要泡到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得大家都住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一天馬上就要過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的樂趣現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是馬上要睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴真是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上不單單只是睡覺的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一整晚努力的修行也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:21.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那凜到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帶行人大人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和他睡在同一被窩裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後一整晚在裡面卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是睡覺技能的特訓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍  我覺得不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  大姐頭不能偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想…想和公子…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃也想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在說很大膽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  行人和我同一個房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起睡的應該是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴不是每晚都睡一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  讓我們一晚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在還沒出嫁之前女孩子怎麼就能做出這樣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家還是未成年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話真是沒完沒了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡輪到我出場了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你淺薄的智慧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正起不到什麼作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼有什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  在行人洗澡回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請先回自己的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後只剩下給行人的信而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,信…要寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想與你一起共渡良宵  請來我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說  讓行人自己來選
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是挑戰書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  也許行人會誰都不選獨自一人去空房間睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼讓它們去空房間待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等行人來了把他趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人最喜歡的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一切將在今晚揭曉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人…最喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼  當然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  也許是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凜才不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照其行動規律來看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會假扮成某人然後混到大家裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,窺視等待引發下次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼的話  請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是否是假貨  我會識破他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  真不愧是科學的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼特殊的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  只是想一個一個扯她們的臉來確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐要是去扯的話  就算是真的皮膚也會扯掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜小姐傷害了客人  該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼原始的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有更加科學性的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根據紅外線透視
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根據聲紋和體溫的個體識別之類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能有那麼便利的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是SF
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:31.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,(SF：Science  Fiction  超現實的作品)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為朔夜小姐的存在本身已經是SF了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在這裡不能依靠科學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠直接的方法來把他逼到絕境了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直接的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  對偵探來說最大的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是頂頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,(頂頭：相撲和摔跤的格鬥手段之一，用自己的頭部頂向對手進行攻擊)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是用頭腦  也就是推理力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等著吧  紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受這挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會來…不會來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是練習  練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不能在公子面前太隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也得稍微注重下儀表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  怎麼還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了的話玩什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  已經看過信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的人所在的地方  會是誰的房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這難道是宮本武藏打倒佐佐木小次郎時的戰法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁心智混亂之時忽然閃現一口氣決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不會上當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了尖叫  過來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍小姐  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,師…傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是因為激烈的按摩而動彈不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼按摩會那麼激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來曾有什麼人在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人類按摩椅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是誰會做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是紅夜叉  千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了  真正的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那邀請帖是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在剛才綾音犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍就是第二個犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去  就會出現第三  第四個犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會再讓你擅自妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事情嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和行人單獨兩人渡過一夜的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會這樣撲過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣吻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,背後奇癢無比  難過死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手卻夠不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  再下面點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音皮膚真美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人…怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是因為太癢而進入了妄想世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也許會稍微輕鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉那傢伙接下來打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在新的犧牲者出現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點阻止的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是梅梅小姐的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:12:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什麼沾在臉上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道又是山藥汁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  身體有什麼地方癢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…梅梅你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你選擇我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…雖然還不值得誇耀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  忽然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是平常害羞的梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:35.44,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,讓行人大人看到害羞的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給那孩子所塗的不是山藥汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給那孩子塗的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦沾到便會立即想做H的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蘑菇泥汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然解毒藥在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但看來少年也不是不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅拜託你們倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.34,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫醒有點過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不使用這發笑的藥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這回不讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯  就是這個狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  剛才開始就那麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不是睡不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  尿床了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個敏捷的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡應該不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  是凜的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凜沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼回來這裡  命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為姐姐不帶我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公子  你選擇我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那像大叔一樣的毫無疑問是真正的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那樣的話只能一個個找了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒理由就被打出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來梅梅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朔夜這樣打了她一下就讓她睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才上面有可疑的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  在二樓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特大紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  還醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是看了信而過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我放心了  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我最喜歡的人是小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等  行人你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人吧  怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那給你看證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是剛才所說的紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴的話  能分清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟每天都一起生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這個行人  和平常的感覺有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊  仔細看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我適可而止  離開小鈴身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺…殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…這時候一般應該互相證明自己是真的才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這個是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰理你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點玩過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓你逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經窮途末路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然在小說裡不清楚你是誰就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我會在這裡揭穿你的真實面目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然沒有注意到被引誘上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有懼高症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然怕的動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前邀請來的男人還能再稍微有點樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你絕對做不到像那個男人那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不許…說絕對做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  解毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要…要落下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如傳言中那樣是個很有趣的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得那孩子會如此中意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得湧出了創作欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…總有一天會在滿月之時再會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓他跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑那麼點洞察力就像揭穿我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他不服輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次見面時還是小心點比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有時是會使用忍者招術的怪人紅夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有時以那事件為基礎而寫小說神秘的作家靜丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過其真實身份是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千影  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這試煉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如千影所說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很適合第二代主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,令人期待的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然怪人的宿敵就該是擁有強烈的不服輸精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又能看到靜丸的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的讀者都會非常高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過無論怎麼說  已經約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會再次寫新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和靜丸最重要的書迷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扮演紅夜叉並開始寫小說的契機是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了引起那位喜歡推理小說的書迷的注意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭  我會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經早上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是不知道行人選擇了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺是有點遺憾卻又松了一口氣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣  我們噩夢般的一晚結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  紅夜叉的犧牲者太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉  這憤怒總有一天會償還給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天  要揭穿你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:12.14,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,月見亭的殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺自己作為小說的原型  心情好複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.78,0:23:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且話說回來靜丸到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道  是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘還是保持那神秘比較好  這才是推理小說的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅夜叉也是  靜丸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及女人也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
